Please try an example like this:

1. Use a program to monitor the memory - ex. kpm;
2. Call the spreadsheet program;
3. Enter an integer (let's say 3) in ALL cells of
columns A and B;
4. In cell C1 enter =A1*B1;
5. Copy this cell (C1) to all cells of column C;
6. Look at the time it took and how much memory was consumed.
7. Now kill the spreadsheed program and restart it again.
8. Repeat all steps 1-6 except the step 3.
9. Compare the memory and time consumed with those of step 6. 

